    "And for all other studies we could analyse, our GPT sample did not replicate either the original result or the corresponding Many Labs 2 result.",
    "The effect sizes found by the original studies, the Many Labs 2 replications, and our GPT replications are listed in Table 1.",
    "The verbal descriptions of the effects, whether Many Labs 2 successfully replicated the original findings, and whether our GPT sample successfully replicated the original findings and the Many Labs 2 findings, can be found in Table 2.",
    "The \"correct answer\" effect Unexpectedly, we could not analyse six of the 14 studies in the manner we had originally planned in our pre-registration.",
